{
  "texts": [
    "For nodes has no sibling nodes with a negative score, like A1, we sample and pair them with a negative example.",
    "There are three methods for sampling negative examples:",
    "• Select a Finish node to ensure that its path is marked as \"Not Pass\", such as ⟳ and ×.",
    "• Select a node from another tool to ensure that its path is marked as \"Not Match\", such as C1 and C2.",
    "• If the history steps do not match the instruction, the node can be selected to end its path at \"Pass & Not Match\"."
  ]
}